title: Designing Generative NFT Art with Jeremy Booth
description: Jeremy Booth joins Ben and Joshua to discuss the ins and outs of generative NFT art in the metaverse, his new NFT project called Bushidos, and his creative journey from freelance to working at full-time as a product illustrator at Coinbase.
